Package author: Andrei Salnikov

Please describe any modifications that you made to the package in the
reverse time order.

Tag: V00-00-07
2012-07-24 Andy Salnikov
- rhel6/gcc44 migration, added missing headers

Tag: V00-00-05
2009-10-09 Andy Salnikov
- more fixes needed for 64-bit platform, C int type is not supported 
  by ODBC directly, need to remap it it to long type

Tag: V00-00-04
2009-08-25 Andy Salnikov
- on 64 bit platform SQLBIGINT clashes with long type, will disable
  SQLBIGINT support for now

Tag: V00-00-03
2009-05-19 Igor Gaponenko
- support for 64-bit integer collumns (C++ types: 'long long'
  and 'long long unsigned')

Tag: V00-00-02
2008-12-18 Andy Salnikov
- implemented array fetching
  - OdbcResult::fetch() returns the number of the rows fetched
- implemented OdbcConnection::tables()
- added date/time types for parameters/column vars

Tag: V00-00-01
2008-12-17 Andy Salnikov
- first import of the package into repository, minimally working version

